            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-white mb-3" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusVenues.astro:6eg5u4">St. Raphael Resort</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusVenues.astro:pddjyi">Beachfront luxury with a private chapel and stunning Mediterranean views, perfect for large or intimate weddings.</p>
